query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it1.info in ('rating','LD length','LD official retail price','LD release date','LD sharpness','LD certification','LD subtitles','LD master format','LD aspect ratio','tech info') AND cct1.kind in ('crew','complete','complete+verified') AND it2.info not in ('nick names','salary history','LD frequency response','LD language','LD catalog number','LD official retail price','birth date','LD picture format','birth name','books','LD original title','LD release country','LD number of chapter stops','tech info','admissions','adaption','LD color information','LD laserdisc title','height') AND mi.info not in ('Swiss German','Turkish','Greenlandic','Chinese','Kyrgyz','Swedish','Persian','Urdu','Vietnamese','Slovak','Zulu') AND cct2.kind in ('complete','complete+verified','cast') AND n.gender in ('m') AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' AND t.production_year < 1992
